com.twiddles.ganesha.gui
Class GUIEvent

java.lang.Object
  com.twiddles.ganesha.gui.GUIEvent
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.awt.event.ActionListener, java.util.EventListener
class GUIEvent
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.awt.event.ActionListener

ActionListener for various menu and toolbar items. This ActionListener can be attached to menu or toolbar items that need to call methods in the GUI class.
